---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
import { Image } from "astro:assets"
---

<Layout title="Happy Father's Day Dad!!">
	<main class="px-10 pt-10 pb-[5rem] h-screen bg-zinc-100">
		<div class="font-semibold text-xl text-left">
			<h1>Happy <span class="text-blue-500">Fathers Day</span>!</h1>
			<h1>
				<span class="border-b-blue-500 border-b-2">Thank You</span> for being
				my <span class="font-bold text-blue-600" id="typewriter"></span>
			</h1>
		</div>
		<div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-10">
			<Image
				class="rounded-md"
				src="/main-pic.jpg"
				alt="Dad n Me"
				width="300"
				height="200"
			/>
		</div>

		<div
			class="rounded-md mt-12 font-light text-lg bg-slate-600 p-5 text-white">
			<h1 class="font-semibold">Hi dad! 👋</h1>First of all, thank you for
			everything that you have done over this year dad. You have been
			incredibly supportive throughout so many challenges that I've gone
			through and I'd like to point them out.
		</div>

		<div
			class="rounded-md mt-12 font-light text-lg bg-slate-600 p-5 text-white">
			<h1 class="font-semibold">Heart Break 💔</h1>
			Thank you for supporting me throughout my breakup with Jessica. I remember
			each time that you gave me advice throughout that summer.
		</div>
		<div
			class="rounded-md mt-12 font-light text-lg bg-slate-600 p-5 text-white">
			<h1 class="font-semibold">Coming Back to CA 🇺🇸</h1>
			Thank you for letting Birdy come with me to CA and financing her trip.
			I appreciated you giving me the oppurtunity to return here with someone
			else.
		</div>
		<div
			class="rounded-md mt-12 font-light text-lg bg-slate-600 p-5 text-white">
			<h1 class="font-semibold">Heart Break #2 💔</h1>
			Thank you for supporting me across the ocean when I sent you regular
			voice calls and you supporting my decision to go to therapy.
		</div>
		<div
			class="rounded-md mt-12 font-light text-lg bg-slate-600 p-5 text-white">
			<h1 class="font-semibold">Finance 💰</h1>
			Thank you for teaching me valuable skills in planning budgeting and being
			able to calculate numbers quickly. My budgeting skills have gotten much
			better and I'm able to think quickly regarding money better too.
		</div>
		<div
			class="rounded-md mt-12 font-light text-lg bg-slate-600 p-5 text-white">
			<h1 class="font-semibold">Advice 📖</h1>
			Thank you for giving me advice regarding so many topics. From love, money,
			to just daily life tips. I have learned so much from you this year.
		</div>
		<div
			class="rounded-md mt-12 font-light text-lg bg-slate-600 p-5 text-white">
			<h1 class="font-semibold">Career 📖</h1>
			Thank you for helping me find oppurtunities like the Google referral.
			You have also reviewed my resume countless times and given feedback.
			You have also brainstormed with me ways to improve my career. I appreciate
			everything you have done to help me advance my career!
		</div>
		<div class="text-black text-lg my-10">
			<h1 class="font-semibold">Thank You 🙏</h1>
			Thank you for reading this, and Happy <span class="text-blue-500"
				>Fathers Day</span
			>!! Enjoy your stay in the USA!
		</div>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style></style>

<script>
	import Typewriter from "typewriter-effect/dist/core"
	const typewriter = new Typewriter("#typewriter", {
		strings: [
			"Dad.",
			"Role Model.",
			"Inspiration.",
			"Supporter.",
			"Guardian.",
		],
		autoStart: true,
		loop: true,
	})
	typewriter.pauseFor(1000).start()
</script>
